    "en": {
      "title": "America has offered to help Sri Lanka",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "US Ambassador to Sri Lanka Julie Sung has said that the United States is ready to help solve the economic crisis in the country.",
        "He made this known through a post on his official Twitter page.",
        "Also, Julie Sung said that the United States has offered to help in this way based on the friendly relationship between the United States and Sri Lanka. (a)"
      ],
